# Per-Dockerfile ignore (BuildKit: <dockerfile-path>.dockerignore). Build context is the repo root, so trim it
# hard — only the manifests + the source COPY'd in the Dockerfile matter. Kept under infra/ (no repo-root file).
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/dist
**/build
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.expo
**/coverage
app/ios
app/android
e2e/artifacts
e2e/fixtures/tapes/*.live.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/.DS_Store
.gcloud
service-account*.json
infra/terraform
